<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
    <head>
        <title>Bualatok</title>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-TX8t27EcRE3e/ihU7zmQxVncDAy5uIKz4rEkgIXeMed4M0jlfIDPvg6uqKI2xXr2" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.4.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lobster&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
        
    </head>
    <body class="d-flex flex-column min-vh-100">
        

        
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light shadow">
            <a href="/home" class="navbar-brand col-auto logo mr-lg-5">BualaTok</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler navbar-light" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#main-navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse align-items-center" id="main-navigation">
                <div class="container">
                    <!-- Action temporal: se tiene que procesar la busqueda adecuadamente -->
                    <form class="col-auto col-lg-12 mb-0 mb-lg-0 me-lg-3" action="/search">
                        <input type="search" class="form-control form-control-dark d-none d-lg-flex d-xl-flex  rounded-input" placeholder="Search..." id="psearch" name="q">
                    </form>
                </div>
                
                <ul class="navbar-nav col-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/search">Buscar productos</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <div class="dropdown">
                            <a href="" class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" id="dropdownProductButton" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
                                Productos
                            </a>
                            <div class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right" aria-labelledby="dropdownProductButton">
                                <a class="dropdown-item" href="/newitem">Registrar producto</a>
                                <a class="dropdown-item" href="/itemlist">Mis productos</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                    </li>
                </ul>
                
            </div>
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 dropdown mr-4 ">
                
                <a href="#" class="d-block text-dark link-dark text-decoration-none dropdown-toggle pt-1" id="dropdownMenuButton" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
                    {{username}}
                    <img src="images/fg-avatar-anonymous-user-retina.png" alt="user" width="32" height="32" class="rounded-circle">
                </a>
                <div class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right" aria-labelledby="dropdownMenuButton">
                  <a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Opciones</a>
                  <a class="dropdown-item" href="/logout">Logout</a>
                </div>
              </div>
        </nav>

        <header class="page-header header container-fluid text-center">
            <div class="header-dim">
                <div class="header-description text-light">
                    <h1>BualaTok</h1>
                    <p>La web para vender, comprar y cambiar lo que te sobra</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="container pt-3">
            <h2 class="text-center">Categorías más populares</h2>
            <div class="row text-center mt-5 justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-lg-auto col-12 card_cat">
                    <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none link-dark text-dark">
                        <div>
                            <img src="images/coupe-car.svg" alt="car" height="100" width="100">
                        </div>
                        Vehículos
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-auto col-12 card_cat">
                    <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none link-dark text-dark">
                        <div>
                            <img src="images/playstation.svg" alt="car" height="100" width="100">
                        </div>
                        Videojuegos
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-auto col-12 card_cat">
                    <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none link-dark text-dark">
                        <div>
                            <img src="images/tshirt.svg" alt="car" height="100" width="100">
                        </div>
                        Ropa
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-auto col-12 card_cat">
                    <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none link-dark text-dark">
                        <div>
                            <img src="images/laptop.svg" alt="car" height="100" width="100">
                        </div>
                        Ordenadores
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-auto col-12 card_cat">
                    <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none link-dark text-dark">
                        <div>
                            <img src="images/smartphone.svg" alt="car" height="100" width="100">
                        </div>
                        Dispositivos móviles
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-auto col-12 card_cat">
                    <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none link-dark text-dark">
                        <div>
                            <img src="images/tv.svg" alt="car" height="100" width="100">
                        </div>
                        TV, Audio y Foto
                    </a>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>


        <footer class="footer mt-auto py-3 bg-light">
            <div class="container text-center">

                    <div class="container text-center">
                        © 2021 Copyright: lol - Created by Gonzalo Nicolas (Emdien) -
                        <a href="https://github.com/Emdien" target="_blank">My github</a>
                    </div>  
                    <div class="container text-center">Icons made by <a href="https://www.freepik.com" title="Freepik">Freepik</a> and <a href="https://www.flaticon.com/authors/darius-dan" title="Darius Dan">Darius Dan</a> from <a href="https://www.flaticon.com/" title="Flaticon">www.flaticon.com</a></div>

            </div>
        </footer>
